{
    "IgxDropDownItemBase": {
        "comment": {
            "shortText": [
                "`<igx-drop-down-item>` は `<igx-drop-down>` コンテナの行項目のためのコンテナです。"
            ]
        },
        "properties": {
            "value": {
                "comment": {
                    "text": [
                        "```typescript",
                        "// usage in IgxDropDownItemComponent",
                        "// get",
                        "let mySelectedItemValue = this.dropdown.selectedItem.value;",
                        "",
                        "// set",
                        "let mySelectedItem = this.dropdown.selectedItem;",
                        "mySelectedItem.value = { id: 123, name: 'Example Name' }",
                        "",
                        "// usage in IgxComboItemComponent",
                        "// get",
                        "let myComboItemValue = this.combo.items[0].value;",
                        "```",
                        ""
                    ],
                    "shortText": [
                        "項目がデータにバインドされる場合、項目の値を取得または設定します。"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "isHeader": {
                "comment": {
                    "text": [
                        "```html",
                        " <!--set-->",
                        " <igx-dropdown-item *ngFor=\"let item of items\">",
                        "     <div *ngIf=\"items.indexOf(item) === 5; then item.isHeader = true\">",
                        "         {{item.field}}",
                        "          </div>",
                        " </igx-drop-down-item>",
                        "```",
                        ""
                    ],
                    "shortText": [
                        "指定した項目がヘッダーかどうかを取得または設定します。",
                        "```typescript",
                        " // get",
                        " let mySelectedItem = this.dropdown.selectedItem;",
                        " let isMyItemHeader = mySelectedItem.isHeader;",
                        "```"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "disabled": {
                "comment": {
                    "text": [
                        "```typescript",
                        " // get",
                        " let mySelectedItem = this.dropdown.selectedItem;",
                        " let myItemIsDisabled = mySelectedItem.disabled;",
                        "```",
                        "",
                        "```html",
                        " <igx-drop-down-item *ngFor=\"let item of items\" disabled={{!item.disabled}}>",
                        "     <div>",
                        "         {{item.field}}",
                        "     </div>",
                        " </igx-drop-down-item>",
                        "```",
                        ""
                    ],
                    "shortText": [
                        "指定した項目が無効かどうかを取得または設定します。"
                    ]
                }
            }
        },
        "methods": {},
        "accessors": {
            "isSelected": {
                "getter": {
                    "comment": {
                        "text": [
                            "```typescript",
                            " let mySelectedItem = this.dropdown.selectedItem;",
                            " let isMyItemSelected = mySelectedItem.isSelected; // true",
                            "```",
                            ""
                        ],
                        "shortText": [
                            "項目がドロップダウンで現在選択されている項目かどうかを取得します。"
                        ]
                    }
                }
            },
            "isFocused": {
                "getter": {
                    "comment": {
                        "shortText": [
                            "指定した項目がフォーカスされるかどうかを取得または設定します。",
                            "```typescript",
                            " let mySelectedItem = this.dropdown.selectedItem;",
                            " let isMyItemFocused = mySelectedItem.isFocused;",
                            "```"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "setter": {
                    "comment": {
                        "shortText": [
                            "```html",
                            " <igx-drop-down-item *ngFor=\"let item of items\" isFocused={{!item.isFocused}}>",
                            "     <div>",
                            "         {{item.field}}",
                            "     </div>",
                            " </igx-drop-down-item>",
                            "```"
                        ]
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "functions": {}
    }
}
